casebody.data:
LAND OF LINCOLN MUTUAL HEALTH INSURANCE COMPANY, an Illinois Nonprofit Mutual Insurance Corporation, petitioner,
v.
UNITED STATES. No. 18-1038. Supreme Court of the United States June 24, 2019.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Federal Circuit granted. The case is consolidated, and a total of one hour is allotted for oral argument.
